overview.en: FarmaTrust (FTT) is a cryptocurrency and operates on the Ethereum platform. FarmaTrust has a current supply of 1,000,000,000 with 600,000,000 in circulation. The last known price of FarmaTrust is 0.01931904 USD and is up 4.09 over the last 24 hours. More information can be found at https://www.farmatrust.com/.
